head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths CARACCI, JOSEPHINE (NEE CULCASI)

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths CARACCI, JOSEPHINE (NEE CULCASI)

block.p: CARACCI-Josephine (nee Culcasi). On September 30, 2000, of Bay Terrace, NY. Beloved wife of Frank. Adored mother of Joseph and Philip and their spouses, Debora and Yvonne. Loving grandmother of Danny, Tina and Emily. Dear sister of Nancy La Marca. Employed 30 years by Commercial Travelers and the Equitable Insurance Company. Reposing at the Frederick Funeral Home of Flushing, Northern Blvd at 193rd St. Visiting hours Monday and Tuesday, 2-5 and 7-10 PM. Mass of Christian Burial, Our Lady of the Blessed Sacrament Church, Bayside, NY, at 10:15 AM, Wednesday. Interment St. John's Cemetery, Middle Village, NY.
